                cursor: "pointer"
            }).on("pointerdown", this.onDiscordClick.bind(this)),
            this.instaBtn = this.create(this.leaderInfo.x + 60 * this.scaleFact, this.leaderInfo.y + 110 * this.scaleFact, "icons3", "instaBtn0000").setScale(.5 * this.scaleFact).setScrollFactor(0).setDepth(1002).setInteractive({
                cursor: "pointer"
            }).on("pointerdown", this.onInstaClick.bind(this)),
            this.replayBtn = this.create(.5 * this.c_w, this.leaderInfo.y + 280 * this.scaleFact, "icons3", "replayBtn0000").setScale(.5 * this.scaleFact).setScrollFactor(0).setDepth(1002).setInteractive({
                cursor: "pointer"
            }).once("pointerdown", this.replayGame.bind(this)),
            this.scoreTxt.setText(`${jn.scoreTotal < 10 ? "0" : ""}${jn.scoreTotal}`)
        }
        fillData(t, e, i=!1) {
            this.leaderBG = this.create(.5 * this.c_w - 190 * this.scaleFact * (e < 4 ? 1 : -1) * (i ? 0 : 1), i ? this.userTitle.y + 75 * this.scaleFact : this.extraTop + 350 * this.scaleFact + e % 4 * 100 * this.scaleFact, "icons3", `placeHolder${i ? "2" : ""}0000`).setScale(.55 * this.scaleFact).setDepth(1002).setScrollFactor(0),
            t.rank <= 3 ? this.rankIcon = this.create(this.leaderBG.x - (i ? 300 : 130) * this.scaleFact, this.leaderBG.y - 15 * this.scaleFact, "icons3", `place${t.rank}0000`).setScale(.5 * this.scaleFact).setDepth(1002).setScrollFactor(0) : (this.rankTxt1 = this.scene.make.text({
                x: this.leaderBG.x - (i ? 320 : 160) * this.scaleFact,
                y: this.leaderBG.y + 2 * this.scaleFact,
                text: "#",
                origin: {
                    x: 0,
                    y: .5
                },
                style: {
                    font: (jn.isMobile,
                    String(15 * this.scaleFact / .5) + "px TT_Neue_Condensed_Bold"),
                    fill: "#ffffff",
                    align: "center",
                    stroke: "#000000",
                    strokeThickness: 8 * this.scaleFact
                }
            }).setDepth(1002).setScrollFactor(0),
            this.add(this.rankTxt1),
            this.rankTxt2 = this.scene.make.text({
                x: this.leaderBG.x - (i ? 276 : 138) * this.scaleFact,
                y: this.leaderBG.y,
                text: t.rank,
                origin: {
                    x: 0,
                    y: .5
                },
                style: {
                    font: (jn.isMobile,
                    String(18 * this.scaleFact / .5) + "px TT_Neue_Condensed_Bold"),
                    fill: "#ffffff",
                    align: "center",
                    weight: "1800",
                    stroke: "#000000",
                    strokeThickness: 10 * this.scaleFact
                }
            }).setDepth(1002).setScrollFactor(0),
            this.add(this.rankTxt2)),
            this.name = this.scene.make.text({
                x: this.leaderBG.x - (i ? 0 : 80) * this.scaleFact,
                y: this.leaderBG.y,
                text: t.name.substr(0, 10),
                origin: {
                    x: i ? .5 : 0,
                    y: .5
                },
                style: {
                    font: (jn.isMobile,
                    String(18 * this.scaleFact / .5) + "px TT_Neue_Condensed_DemiBold"),
                    fill: "#ffffff",
                    align: "center",
                    stroke: "#000000",
                    strokeThickness: 10 * this.scaleFact
                }
            }).setDepth(1002).setScrollFactor(0),
            this.add(this.name),
            this.score = this.scene.make.text({
                x: this.leaderBG.x + (i ? 320 : 160) * this.scaleFact,
                y: this.leaderBG.y,
                text: t.score,
                origin: {
                    x: 1,
                    y: .5
                },
                style: {
                    font: (jn.isMobile,
                    String(18 * this.scaleFact / .5) + "px TT_Neue_Condensed_Bold"),
                    fill: "#FFD000",
                    align: "center",
                    stroke: "#000000",
                    strokeThickness: 10 * this.scaleFact
                }
            }).setDepth(1002).setScrollFactor(0),
            this.add(this.score)
        }
        goBack() {
            this.emitter.emit("leader:back")
        }
    }

            this.layer3 = this.add.image(this.extraLeftPer, this.c_h - this.extraTop, "layer3_4", "layer3_10000").setOrigin(0, 1).setScale(.0016 * (this.c_w - 2 * this.extraLeftPer) * .75),
            this.layer2 = this.add.image(.5 * this.c_w, this.c_h - this.extraTop - 330 * this.scaleFact, "icons2", "layer20000").setBlendMode(Phaser.BlendModes.SCREEN).setScale(.0016 * (this.c_w - 2 * this.extraLeftPer) * .75),

            this.title1 = this.add.image(this.extraLeftPer + .245 * (this.c_w - 2 * this.extraLeftPer), this.extraTop + 180 * this.scaleFact, "icons3", "title10000").setDepth(1002).setScale(96e-5 * (this.c_w - 2 * this.extraLeftPer)).setScrollFactor(0),
            this.title2 = this.add.image(.5 * this.c_w, this.title1.y + this.title1.scaleY * this.title1.height * .05, "icons3", "title20000").setDepth(1002).setOrigin(.5, 0).setScale(96e-5 * (this.c_w - 2 * this.extraLeftPer)).setScrollFactor(0),
            this.characterGr = this.add.group();
            const t = 280 * this.scaleFact;
            if (this.nameText = this.make.text({
                x: .5 * this.c_w,
                y: .5 * this.c_h - 165 * this.scaleFact,
                text: this.names[this.itemIndex].toUpperCase(),

                    stroke: "#0b1946",
                    strokeThickness: 10 * this.scaleFact
                }
            }).setAlpha(1).setScale(1).setDepth(1100).setScrollFactor(0),
            this.platform = this.add.image(.5 * this.c_w, .5 * this.c_h + 425 * this.scaleFact, "icons3", "platform0000").setDepth(1e3).setScale(.55 * this.scaleFact).setScrollFactor(0),
            this.items.forEach( (e, i) => {
                this["player" + e] = this.characterGr.create(.5 * this.c_w + t * (i - 2), .5 * this.c_h + ("blob" == e ? 420 : 400) * this.scaleFact, "standing", e + "_standing0000").setDepth(1001).setData("itemIndex", i).setData("posIndex", i).setInteractive({
                    cursor: "pointer"
                }).setOrigin(.5, .95).setAlpha(2 == i ? 1 : 0 == i || i == this.items.length - 1 ? 0 : .25).setScale(this.scaleFact * (2 == i ? 1.2 : 1)),
                this.itemLockStatus[i] && this["player" + e].setTint(0),
                (this.itemLockStatus[i] || 3 == i) && (this[`player${e}UnlockTxt`] = this.make.text({
                    x: .5 * this.c_w + t * (i - 2),
                    y: .5 * this.c_h - (this.isUnlocked ? 20 : 80) * this.scaleFact,
                    text: this.isUnlocked ? "Unlocked" : `UNLOCKS ONLY AFTER\nSCORING ${jn.revealThreshold}+ POINTS`,
                    origin: {
                        x: .5,
                        y: .5
                    },
                    style: {
                        font: (jn.isMobile,
                        String((this.isUnlocked ? 25 : 15) * this.scaleFact / .5) + "px TT_Neue_Condensed_DemiBold"),
                        fill: "#ffffff",
                        align: "center",
                        stroke: "#0b1946",
                        lineSpacing: -8 * this.scaleFact,
                        strokeThickness: 10 * this.scaleFact
                    }
                }).setAlpha(1).setDepth(1001).setScrollFactor(0),
                this["player" + e].setData("UnlockTxt", this[`player${e}UnlockTxt`]),
                this[`player${e}Lock`] = this.add.image(.5 * this.c_w + t * (i - 2) + 100 * this.scaleFact, .5 * this.c_h - 80 * this.scaleFact, "Lock").setAlpha(0).setVisible(!this.isUnlocked).setDepth(1002).setScale(.5 * this.scaleFact),
                this["player" + e].setData("lockIcon", this[`player${e}Lock`]))
            }
            ),
            this.floor = this.matter.add.rectangle(.5 * this.c_w, this.c_h - this.extraTop - 250 * this.scaleFact, this.c_w, 100 * this.scaleFact, {
                isStatic: !0
            }),
            this.playerNext = this.add.image(.5 * this.c_w + 250 * this.scaleFact, .5 * this.c_h + 150 * this.scaleFact, "icons3", "arrow0000").setInteractive({
                cursor: "pointer"
            }).setDepth(1002).on("pointerdown", this.changeCharacter.bind(this, 1, !1)).setScale(.7 * this.scaleFact),
            this.playerPrev = this.add.image(.5 * this.c_w - 250 * this.scaleFact, .5 * this.c_h + 150 * this.scaleFact, "icons3", "arrow0000").setInteractive({
                cursor: "pointer"
            }).setDepth(1002).on("pointerdown", this.changeCharacter.bind(this, -1, !1)).setScale(.7 * -this.scaleFact, .7 * this.scaleFact),
            this.header = new vs(this),
            this.header.setUp(),
            this.header.init(!1, !1, !1, !0),
            this.leaderboard = new ms(this),
            this.leaderboard.setUp(),
            this.leaderboard.init(),
            this.leaderboard.setVisible(!1),
            this.cameras.main.fadeIn(500),
            this.playBtn = this.add.sprite(.5 * this.c_w, this.c_h - this.extraTop - 150 * this.scaleFact, "icons3", "startBtn0000").setInteractive({
                cursor: "pointer"
            }).once("pointerdown", () => {
                setTimeout( () => {
                    jn.musicEnabled && !jn.BGAudio.isPlaying && jn.BGAudio.play()
                }
                , 250),
                jn.musicEnabled && jn.tapAudio.play(),
                gs.kill(),
                this.cameras.main.fadeOut(500),
                jn.animateButton.call(this, this.playBtn, !1),
                setTimeout( () => {
                    localStorage.setItem("navIndex", this.navIndex),
                    this.scene.start("Game")
                }
                , 750)
            }
            ).setScale(.55 * this.scaleFact).setScrollFactor(0).setDepth(1002),
            this.particleEmitter = this.add.particles(this.c_w, 0, "particles", {
                frame: ["particle10000", "particle20000", "particle30000", "particle40000", "particle50000", "particle60000"],
                frequency: 1e3,
                speedX: {
                    min: -300 * this.scaleFact,
                    max: -500 * this.scaleFact
                },
                speedY: {
                    min: -200 * this.scaleFact,
                    max: 200 * this.scaleFact
                },
                rotate: {
                    min: -10,
                    max: 10
                },
                scale: this.scaleFact,
                alpha: {
                    start: 1,
                    end: .75
                },
                lifespan: 3e3,
                rotate: {
                    min: 0,
                    max: 360
                },
                angularVelocity: {
                    min: -180,
                    max: 180
                },
                gravityY: 200 * this.scaleFact * 0,
                emitZone: {
                    type: "edge",
                    source: new Phaser.Geom.Line(0,0,this.c_w,this.c_h),
                    quantity: 20
                },
                emitting: !0
            }).setScrollFactor(0).setBlendMode(Phaser.BlendModes.SCREEN).setDepth(100),
            "undefined" != typeof localStorage)
                if (this.isUnlocked)
                    this.changeCharacter(1, !0);
                else if (localStorage.getItem("navIndex")) {
                    let t = parseInt(localStorage.getItem("navIndex"));
                    1 == t && (t = 0),
                    this.changeCharacter(t, !0)
                }
        }
        changeCharacter(t, e=!1) {
            if (!this.canChange || this.charSelected)
                return;
            jn.musicEnabled && !e && jn.rollAudio.play(),
            this.canChange = !1,
            this.btnTO && clearTimeout(this.btnTO),
            t > 0 ? this.playerNext.setFrame("arrow_10000") : this.playerPrev.setFrame("arrow_10000"),
            this.btnTO = setTimeout( () => {
                this.playerNext.setFrame("arrow0000"),
                this.playerPrev.setFrame("arrow0000")
            }
            , 125);
            const i = this.characterGr.children.entries
              , n = this.items.length
              , r = .5 * this.c_w
              , s = 350 * this.scaleFact;
            i.forEach( (e, i) => {
                let o = e.getData("posIndex");
                o = (o - t + n) % n,
                e.setData("posIndex", o),
                e.__targetX = r + s * (o - 2),
                e.__targetAlpha = 2 === o ? 1 : 0 == o ? 0 : .25,
                e.__targetScale = this.scaleFact * (2 === o ? 1.2 : 1),
                e.setOrigin(.5, .95)
            }
            );
            const o = i.find(t => 2 === t.getData("posIndex"))
              , a = i.find(t => 0 === t.getData("posIndex"));
            a && (this.navIndex = parseInt(a.getData("itemIndex"))),
            o && (this.itemIndex = o.getData("itemIndex"),
            jn.characterKey = this.items[this.itemIndex]);
            const h = i.filter(t => 2 !== t.getData("posIndex"))
              , l = i.filter(t => 2 === t.getData("posIndex"));
            this.isLocked = this.itemLockStatus[this.itemIndex],
            this.isLocked ? this.playBtn.disableInteractive().setAlpha(.75) : this.playBtn.setInteractive({
                cursor: "pointer"
            }).setAlpha(1),
            this.tweens.add({
                targets: h,
                x: t => t.__targetX,
                alpha: t => t.__targetAlpha,
                scale: t => t.__targetScale,
                duration: e ? 10 : 500,
                ease: Phaser.Math.Easing.Cubic.InOut,
                onUpdate: function() {
                    h.forEach( (t, e) => {
                        const i = t.getData("lockIcon");
                        if (i) {
                            i.x = t.x + 170 * this.scaleFact,
                            i.y = t.y - (this.isUnlocked ? 495 : 459) * this.scaleFact,
                            i.scale = t.scaleX / this.scaleFact / 2,
                            i.alpha = t.alpha;
                            const e = t.getData("UnlockTxt");
                            e && (e.alpha = t.alpha,
                            e.x = t.x,
                            e.y = t.y - (this.isUnlocked ? 495 : 459) * this.scaleFact)
                        }
                    }
                    )
                }
                .bind(this),
                onComplete: () => {
                    this.canChange = !0
                }
            }),
            this.tweens.add({
                targets: l,
                x: t => t.__targetX,
                alpha: 1,
                scale: 1.2 * this.scaleFact,
                duration: e ? 10 : 500,
                ease: Phaser.Math.Easing.Cubic.InOut,
                onUpdate: function() {
                    l.forEach(t => {
                        const e = t.getData("name");
                        e && (e.alpha = t.alpha,
                        e.x = t.x,
                        e.scale = t.scaleX / this.scaleFact);
                        const i = t.getData("lockIcon");
                        if (i) {
                            i.alpha = t.alpha,
                            i.x = t.x + 170 * this.scaleFact,
                            i.y = t.y - (this.isUnlocked ? 495 : 459) * this.scaleFact,
                            i.scale = t.scaleX / this.scaleFact / 2;
                            const e = t.getData("UnlockTxt");
                            e && (e.alpha = t.alpha,
                            e.x = t.x,
                            e.y = t.y - (this.isUnlocked ? 495 : 459) * this.scaleFact)
                        }
                    }
                    )
                }
                .bind(this)
            }),
            this.prevItemIndex = this.itemIndex,
            this.nameText.setText(this.itemLockStatus[this.itemIndex] ? "MYSTERY CHARACTER" : this.names[this.itemIndex].toUpperCase())
        }
        async onPlay() {
            jn.musicEnabled && jn.BGAudio.play(),
            gs.kill(),
            jn.proceeded = !0,
            this.canProceed = !0;
            let t = await ds();
            localStorage.setItem("uuid", t.uid),
            jn.gameTry = t.gameTry,
            jn.bestScore = t.bestScore,
            document.querySelector("#rotate").classList.add("enabled"),
            this.cameras.main.fadeOut(500),
            setTimeout( () => {
                this.jumpTO && clearTimeout(this.jumpTO),
                this.scene.start("Game")
            }
            , 750)
        }
        showLeader() {
            this.footer.setVisible(!1),
            this.header.setVisible(!1),
            this.leaderboard.setVisible(!0),
            this.leaderboard.showLeaderData(),
            this.characterGr.setVisible(!1),
            this.playerNext.setVisible(!1),
            this.playerPrev.setVisible(!1)
        }
        onLeaderBack() {
            this.leaderboard.setVisible(!1),
            this.footer.setVisible(!0),
            this.header.setVisible(!0),
            this.characterGr.setVisible(!0),
            this.playerNext.setVisible(!0),
            this.playerPrev.setVisible(!0)
        }
    }
    class xs extends Phaser.Physics.Matter.Sprite {
        constructor(t, e, i, n, r) {
            super(t, e, i, n, r + "0000"),
            this.scene.add.existing(this),
            this.setDepth(1001),
            this.setFriction(0),
            this.setBounce(0),
            this.setAngularSpeed(0),
            this.setAngularVelocity(0),
            this.playerType = r,
            this.jump = this.jump.bind(this)
        }
        setUp() {
            Kn.call(this, !1),
            this.emitter = gs.getObj(),
            this.emitter.on("game:update", this.update.bind(this)),
            this.emitter.on("game:go_back", () => {
                this.scene.input.off("pointerdown")
            }
            ),
            this.setScale(45e-5 * (this.c_h - 2 * this.extraTop)),
            this.lastObsctacleX = 400,
            this.smoothedDt = 16.6,
            this.setBody({
                type: "rectangle",
                width: this.width * this.scaleX * .6,
                height: this.height * this.scaleY * .4
            }),
            this.setIgnoreGravity(!0),
            this.scene.input.on("pointerdown", this.jump),
            this.scene.matter.world.on("collisionstart", async (t, e, i) => {
                this.controlEnabled && ("obstacle" != e.key && "obstacle" != i.key && ("floor" != e.key && "floor" != i.key || this.isLanded) || (this.gameOver("obstacle" == e.key || "obstacle" == i.key),
                "obstacle" != e.key && "obstacle" != i.key || (this.setAngularSpeed(-.05),
                this.setVelocity(-5 * this.scaleFact, this.body.velocity.y))))
            }
            )
        }
        init() {
            this.isMoving = !1,
            this.isFirstCross = !0,
            this.controlEnabled = !0,
            this.isLanded = !1,
            this.lastObsctacleX = 0,
            this.maxSpeed = {
                value: 0
            }
        }
        update(t) {
            this.isMoving && (this.smoothedDt += .05 * (t - this.smoothedDt),
            this.x += this.maxSpeed.value * this.smoothedDt * this.scaleFact * .7,
            this.x >= this.lastObsctacleX && (this.lastObsctacleX += this.c_w + Math.max(.2, Math.random()) * this.c_w + 400 * this.scaleFact * this.maxSpeed.value,
            this.emitter.emit("obstacle:add", this.lastObsctacleX),
            this.isFirstCross || (this.emitter.emit("scoreboard:add", 1),
            this.maxSpeed.value += .03 * .7,
            jn.musicEnabled && jn.collectAudio.play()),
            this.isFirstCross = !1),
            Math.abs(this.angle) > 15 && (this.angle = 0))
        }
        gameOver(t=!1) {
            this.apiHitCnt = 0,
            this.isMoving = !1,
            this.controlEnabled = !1,
            this.scene.cameras.main.shake(300, .01, .01),
            jn.musicEnabled && jn.hitAudio.play(),
            this.emitter.emit("game:over_ui_update", t),
            setTimeout(async () => {
                jn.gameDataToSent = {
                    gameTry: jn.gameTry,
                    uid: localStorage.getItem("uuid"),
                    score: jn.scoreTotal,
                    characterKey: jn.characterNames[jn.characterKey]
                },
                this.scene.cameras.main.fadeOut(500),
                setTimeout( () => {
                    this.scene.cameras.main.fadeIn(500),
                    this.emitter.emit("game:over")
                }
                , 500),
                await this.sendGameData()
            }
            , 100)
        }
        async sendGameData() {
            try {
                return await async function() {
                    const t = cs({
                        uuid: localStorage.getItem("uuid"),
                        data: jn.gameDataToSent
                    })
                      , e = new FormData;
                    e.append("data", JSON.stringify(t));
                    let i = await us.post("saveGameData.php", e);
                    return i = fs(i),
                    i.data.includes("SQLSTATE") ? i.data : JSON.parse(window.atob(i.data))
                }()
            } catch (t) {
                if (this.apiHitCnt < 5) {
                    this.apiHitCnt++;
                    const t = 1e3;
                    return console.warn(`Retry attempt ${this.apiHitCnt} for sendUserData. Waiting ${t}ms...`),
                    await this.sleep(t),
                    await this.sendGameData()
                }
                return ""
            }
        }
        sleep(t) {
            return new Promise(e => setTimeout(e, t))
        }
        jump(t) {
            this.controlEnabled && (this.y < 100 * this.scaleFact + this.extraTop ? this.gameOver() : (this.isMoving || (this.isMoving = !0,
            this.body.isStatic = !1,
            this.emitter.emit("header:hide_back"),
            this.setIgnoreGravity(!1),
            this.start(),
            this.leanForward()),
            (this.isMoving || jn.gameTry > 1) && jn.musicEnabled && jn.tap2Audio.play(),
            this.isLanded && (this.scene.tweens.killTweensOf(this),
            this.angle = 0,
            this.leanForward()),
            this.isLanded = !1,
            this.play(this.playerType + "_jump"),
            this.setVelocityY(-33)))
        }
        start() {
            this.scene.tweens.add({
                targets: this.maxSpeed,
                value: .75,
                ease: Phaser.Math.Easing.Linear,
                duration: 500
            }),
            this.emitter.emit("particle:start"),
            this.emitter.emit("intro:remove")
        }
        leanForward() {}
    }
    var bs = i(131)
      , ws = i.n(bs);
    class Ts extends Phaser.GameObjects.Group {
        constructor(t) {
            super(t),
            document.querySelector("#submitBtn").addEventListener("click", this.checkIfCanProceed.bind(this)),
            document.querySelector("#replayBtn").addEventListener("click", this.replayGame.bind(this))
        }
        setUp() {
            Kn.call(this, !1),
            this.emitter = gs.getObj()
        }
        init() {
            jn.proceeded = !1
        }
        replayGame() {
            jn.gameTry > 2 || jn.scoreTotal >= 10 || jn.proceeded || jn.userRegistered || (jn.proceeded = !0,
            jn.animateButton.call(this, document.querySelector("#replayBtn"), !0),
            jn.musicEnabled && jn.tapAudio.play(),
            this.scene.cameras.main.fadeOut(500),
            setTimeout( () => {
                gs.kill(),
                this.emitter.emit("game:replay")
            }
            , 500),
            this.showTO && clearTimeout(this.showTO),
            document.querySelector(".register_scr").classList.remove("active2"),
            setTimeout( () => {
                document.querySelector(".register_scr").classList.remove("active")
            }
            , 500))
        }
        showNow() {}
        show() {
            this.apiHitCnt = 0,
            jn.bestScore = Math.max(jn.bestScore, jn.scoreTotal),
            document.querySelector(".register_scr").classList.add("active"),
            this.showTO = setTimeout( () => {
                document.querySelector(".register_scr").classList.add("active2")
            }
            , 100),
            jn.gameTry > 2 || jn.scoreTotal >= 10 ? document.querySelector("#replayBtn").classList.add("disabled") : document.querySelector("#replayBtn").classList.remove("disabled"),
            jn.proceeded = !1
        }
        async checkIfCanProceed() {
            if (jn.proceeded)
                return;
            jn.musicEnabled && jn.tapAudio.play(),
            jn.animateButton.call(this, document.querySelector("#submitBtn"), !0);
            const t = document.querySelector("#nick_name").value.trim().toLowerCase()
              , e = document.querySelector("#email").value.trim();
            if (t.length <= 0)
                return this.showError("Please enter a valid Name."),
                this.canClick = !0,
                !1;
            if (ws.a.check(t))
                return this.showError("Please enter a valid Name."),
                this.canClick = !0,
                !1;
            if (!/^(([^<>()\[\]\\.,;:\s@"]+(\.[^<>()\[\]\\.,;:\s@"]+)*)|(".+"))@((\[[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\.[0-9]{1,3}\])|(([a-zA-Z\-0-9]+\.)+[a-zA-Z]{2,}))$/.test(String(e).toLowerCase()))
                return this.showError("Please enter a valid E-mail."),
                this.canClick = !0,
                !1;
            jn.userDataToSent.name = t,
            jn.userDataToSent.email = e,
            jn.userDataToSent.score = jn.scoreTotal,
            jn.proceeded = !0,
            jn.userRegistered = !0,
            this.canProceed = !0;
            let i = await this.sendUserData();
            if ("object" == typeof i && "409" == String(i.status))
                return this.showError("This player name is already taken."),
                jn.proceeded = !1,
                jn.userRegistered = !1,
                void (this.canProceed = !1);
            "object" == typeof i && (localStorage.setItem("uuid", i.uid),
            jn.bestScore = Math.max(jn.bestScore, parseInt(i.bestScore)),
            i.encryptkey && (jn.gameTry = i.gameTry),
            i.encryptkey && (jn.gameKey = i.encryptkey)),
            document.querySelector(".register_scr").classList.remove("active2"),
            setTimeout( () => {
                document.querySelector(".register_scr").classList.remove("active")
            }
            , 500),
            parseInt(jn.bestScore) >= jn.revealThreshold || parseInt(jn.scoreTotal) >= jn.revealThreshold ? localStorage.setItem("slimeUnlocked", !0) : localStorage.setItem("slimeUnlocked", !1),
            setTimeout( () => {
                this.emitter.emit("score:proceed")
            }
            , 500)
        }
        showError(t) {
            document.getElementById("register_error").innerHTML = t,
            document.getElementById("register_error").classList.add("active"),
            setTimeout( () => {
                document.getElementById("register_error").classList.remove("active")
            }
            , 1500)
        }
        sleep(t) {
            return new Promise(e => setTimeout(e, t))
        }
        async sendUserData() {
            try {
                return await ds()
            } catch (t) {
                if (this.apiHitCnt < 5) {
                    this.apiHitCnt++;
                    const t = 1e3;
                    return console.warn(`Retry attempt ${this.apiHitCnt} for sendUserData. Waiting ${t}ms...`),
                    await this.sleep(t),
                    await this.sendUserData()
                }
                return ""
            }
        }
    }
    class Ss extends Phaser.GameObjects.Group {
        constructor(t) {
            super(t)
        }
        setUp() {

            this.emitter = gs.getObj(),
            this.emitter.on("intro:remove", this.removeIntro.bind(this))
        }
        init() {
            this.introBG = this.scene.add.graphics(),
            this.introBG.setScrollFactor(0),
            this.introBG.fillStyle(0, .5),
            this.introBG.fillRect(0, 0, this.c_w, this.c_h),
            this.introBG.setDepth(1e3),
            this.add(this.introBG),
            this.readyIcon = this.create(.5 * this.c_w, .5 * this.c_h + 290 * this.scaleFact, "icons3", "ready0000").setScale(.5 * this.scaleFact).setScrollFactor(0).setDepth(1e3),
            this.readyTxt = this.scene.make.text({

                },

                    String(20 * this.scaleFact / .5) + "px TT_Neue_Condensed_DemiBold"),
                    fill: "#ffffff",
                    align: "center"
                }
            }).setDepth(1e3).setScrollFactor(0),
            this.add(this.readyTxt),
            this.tapIcon = this.create(.5 * this.c_w + 180 * this.scaleFact, this.c_h - this.extraTop - 840 * this.scaleFact, "icons3", "tapIcon0000").setScale(.5 * this.scaleFact).setScrollFactor(0).setDepth(1e3),
            this.handIcon = this.create(.5 * this.c_w + 200 * this.scaleFact, this.c_h - this.extraTop - 700 * this.scaleFact, "icons3", "tapTxt0000").setScale(.5 * this.scaleFact).setScrollFactor(0).setDepth(1e3),
            this.scene.tweens.add({
                targets: this.handIcon,
                alpha: 0,
                yoyo: !0,
                repeat: -1,
                duration: 100,
                repeatDelay: 250
            })
        }
        removeIntro() {
            this.scene.tweens.killTweensOf(this.handIcon),
            this.destroy(!0, !0),
            jn.musicEnabled && jn.startAudio.play()
        }
    }
    class _s extends Phaser.GameObjects.Group {
        constructor(t) {
            super(t)
        }
        setUp() {
            Kn.call(this, !1),
            this.emitter = gs.getObj(),
            this.emitter.on("game:update", this.update.bind(this)),
            this.layer8Index = {
                max: 9,
                val: 0
            },
            this.layer7Index = {
                max: 5,
                val: 0
            },
            this.layer6Index = {
                max: 5,
                val: 0
            },
            this.layer5Index = {
                max: 5,
                val: 0
            },
            this.layer4Index = {
                max: 6,
                val: 0
            },
            this.layer3Index = {
                max: 4,
                val: 0
            },
            this.layers = []
        }
        init() {
            this.addLayer(1, 8, null, this.c_h - this.extraTop - this.extraLeftPer, 1, 1, .25),
            this.addLayer(2, 7, null, this.c_h - this.extraTop - this.extraLeftPer, 1, 1, .4),
            this.addLayer(3, 6, null, this.c_h - this.extraTop - this.extraLeftPer, 1, 1, .55),
            this.addLayer(4, 5, null, this.c_h - this.extraTop - this.extraLeftPer, 1, 1, .6),
            this.addLayer(5, 4, null, this.extraTop, 0, .75, 1),
            this.addLayer(6, 3, null, this.c_h - this.extraTop, 1, .75, 1),
            this.layer2 = this.create(.5 * this.c_w, this.c_h - this.extraTop - 330 * this.scaleFact, "icons2", "layer20000").setDepth(10).setScrollFactor(0).setBlendMode(Phaser.BlendModes.SCREEN).setScale(.0016 * (this.c_w - 2 * this.extraLeftPer) * .75),
            this.layer1 = this.create(.5 * this.c_w, this.c_h - this.extraTop - 330 * this.scaleFact, "icons2", "layer10000").setDepth(10).setScrollFactor(0).setBlendMode(Phaser.BlendModes.ADD).setScale(.0016 * (this.c_w - 2 * this.extraLeftPer) * .75)
        }
        addLayer(t, e, i, n, r, s, o) {
            let a = this.layers.filter(t => t.getData("layerIndex") == e && !t.active);
            this[`layer${e}Index`].val++,
            this[`layer${e}Index`].val > this[`layer${e}Index`].max && (this[`layer${e}Index`].val = 1),
            !a || a && 0 == a.length ? (this.layerItem = this.create(i ? i.x + i.width * i.scaleX - 2 * this.scaleFact : this.extraLeftPer, i ? i.y : n, e < 5 ? "layer3_4" : `layer${e}_${this[`layer${e}Index`].val}`, e < 5 ? `layer${e}_${this[`layer${e}Index`].val}0000` : null).setDepth(t).setData("layerIndex", e).setData("nextAdded", !1).setData("defScaleMult", s).setData("defScrollFact", o).setScrollFactor(i ? i.scrollFactorX : o).setOrigin(0, i ? i.originY : r).setScale(i ? i.scaleX : .0016 * (this.c_w - 2 * this.extraLeftPer) * s),
            -1 !== [5, 2].indexOf(e) && this.layerItem.setBlendMode(Phaser.BlendModes.SCREEN),
            this.layers.push(this.layerItem)) : (this.layerItem = a[0],
            this.layerItem.setTexture(e < 5 ? "layer3_4" : `layer${e}_${this[`layer${e}Index`].val}`).setFrame(e < 5 ? `layer${e}_${this[`layer${e}Index`].val}0000` : null).setDepth(t).setPosition(i ? i.x + i.width * i.scaleX - 2 * this.scaleFact : this.extraLeftPer, i ? i.y : n).setData("layerIndex", e).setData("nextAdded", !1).setData("defScaleMult", s).setData("defScrollFact", o).setScrollFactor(i ? i.scrollFactorX : o).setOrigin(0, i ? i.originY : r).setScale(i ? i.scaleX : .0016 * (this.c_w - 2 * this.extraLeftPer) * s),
            this.layerItem.setActive(!0).setVisible(!0).setAlpha(1))
        }
        update() {
            this.layers.forEach(t => {
                t.active && ((t.x + t.width * t.scaleX) / t.scrollFactorX - this.scene.cameras.main.scrollX <= this.extraLeftPer - this.c_w && (t.setActive(!1),
                t.setVisible(!1)),
                t.x + t.width * t.scaleX - this.scene.cameras.main.scrollX <= this.extraLeftPer + this.c_w && !t.getData("nextAdded") && (t.setData("nextAdded", !0),
                this.addLayer(t.depth, t.getData("layerIndex"), t, this.c_h - this.extraTop, 1, t.getData("defScaleMult"), t.getData("defScrollFact"))))
            }
            )
        }
    }
    class Es extends Phaser.GameObjects.Group {
        constructor(t) {
            super(t)
        }
        setUp() {
            Kn.call(this, !1),
            this.emitter = gs.getObj(),
            this.emitter.on("obstacle:add", this.addObstacles.bind(this)),
            this.emitter.on("game:update", this.update.bind(this)),
            this.obstacles = []
        }
        init() {}
        addObstacles(t) {
            const e = Math.min(5, Math.ceil(7 * Math.max(.1, Math.random())))
              , i = 7 - e;
            for (let i = 0; i < e; i++) {
                let e = this.obstacles.filter(t => !t.active);
                e.length > 0 ? this.obstacle = e[0] : (this.obstacle = this.scene.matter.add.image(0, 0, "icons2", "obstacle0000", {
                    key: "obstacle",
                    isStatic: !0,
                    isSensor: !0
                }),
                this.obstacles.push(this.obstacle)),
                this.obstacle.setDepth(98).setPosition(t, this.c_h - this.extraTop - 340 * this.scaleFact - 100 * i * (this.c_h - 2 * this.extraTop) * 7e-4).setActive(!0).setVisible(!0).setScale(45e-5 * (this.c_h - 2 * this.extraTop))
            }
            for (let e = 0; e < i; e++) {
                let i = this.obstacles.filter(t => !t.active);
                i.length > 0 ? this.obstacle = i[0] : (this.obstacle = this.scene.matter.add.image(0, 0, "icons2", "obstacle0000", {
                    key: "obstacle",
                    isStatic: !0,
                    isSensor: !0
                }),
                this.obstacles.push(this.obstacle)),
                this.obstacle.setDepth(98).setPosition(t, this.extraTop + 55 * this.scaleFact + 100 * e * (this.c_h - 2 * this.extraTop) * 7e-4).setActive(!0).setVisible(!0).setScale(45e-5 * (this.c_h - 2 * this.extraTop), 45e-5 * -(this.c_h - 2 * this.extraTop))
            }
        }
        update() {
            this.obstacles.forEach(t => {
                t.active && (t.x + t.width * t.scaleX) / t.scrollFactorX - this.scene.cameras.main.scrollX <= this.extraLeftPer && (t.setActive(!1),
                t.setVisible(!1))
            }
            )
        }
    }
    class As extends Phaser.Scene {
        constructor() {
            super({
                key: "Game"
            })
        }
        updateBG() {
            setTimeout( () => {
                const t = jn.scoreTotal;
                let e;
                if (t < 100)
                    e = t < 15 ? 16777215 : t < 40 ? 65280 : 255;
                else {
                    const i = (t - 100) % 50;
                    e = i < 15 ? 16777215 : i < 35 ? 65280 : 255
                }
                if (this.lastTarget === e)
                    return;
                this.lastTarget = e;
                const i = -1 === this.bg.tintTopLeft || 16777215 === this.bg.tintTopLeft ? 16777215 : this.bg.tintTopLeft
                  , n = Phaser.Display.Color.IntegerToColor(i)
                  , r = Phaser.Display.Color.IntegerToColor(e);
                this.colorTween && this.colorTween.stop(),
                this.colorTween = this.tweens.addCounter({
                    from: 0,
                    to: 100,
                    duration: 500,
                    onUpdate: t => {
                        const e = t.getValue()
                          , i = Phaser.Display.Color.Interpolate.ColorWithColor(n, r, 100, e)
                          , s = Phaser.Display.Color.GetColor(i.r, i.g, i.b);
                        this.bg.setTint(s)
                    }
                    ,
                    onComplete: () => {
                        16777215 === e && this.bg.clearTint()
                    }
                })
            }
            , 500)
        }
        create() {
            this.apiHitCnt = 0,
            jn.scoreTotal = 0,
            this.isGameOver = !1,
            Kn.call(this, !0),
            this.emitter = gs.getObj(),
            this.emitter.on("particle:start", this.startParticle.bind(this)),
            this.emitter.on("game:over_ui_update", this.onGameOver.bind(this)),
            this.emitter.on("game:over", this.showFinalScreen.bind(this)),
            this.emitter.on("leader:show", this.showLeader.bind(this)),
            this.emitter.on("game:replay", this.replayGame.bind(this)),
            this.emitter.on("leader:back", this.onLeaderBack.bind(this)),
            this.emitter.on("score:proceed", this.showLeader.bind(this)),
            this.emitter.on("game:go_back", this.goBackHome.bind(this)),
            this.emitter.on("scoreboard:add", this.updateBG.bind(this)),
            this.bg = this.add.image(.5 * this.c_w, .5 * this.c_h, "gameBG").setScrollFactor(0).setScale(83e-5 * (this.c_w - 2 * this.extraLeftPer)),
            this.layerMgr = new _s(this),
            this.layerMgr.setUp(),
            this.layerMgr.init(),
            this.floor = this.matter.add.image(.5 * this.c_w, this.c_h - this.extraTop - 300 * this.scaleFact, "icons2", "floor0000", {
                isStatic: !0,
                key: "floor",
                friction: 0,
                restitution: 0
            }).setScale(.7 * this.scaleFact),
            this.character = new xs(this.matter.world,.5 * this.c_w,.5 * this.c_h,"player",jn.characterKey),
            this.character.setUp(),
            this.character.init(),

            this.header.setUp(),
            this.header.init(!0, !0, !0, !0),
            this.obstacleMgr = new Es(this),
            this.obstacleMgr.setUp(),
            this.obstacleMgr.init(),
            this.gameOver = new Ts(this),
            this.gameOver.setUp(),
            this.gameOver.init(),
            this.leaderboard = new ms(this),
            this.leaderboard.setUp(),
            this.leaderboard.init(),
            this.leaderboard.setVisible(!1),
            this.gameOver.setVisible(!1),
            this.cameras.main.startFollow(this.character, !1, 1, 0, -200 * this.scaleFact, 0),
            this.character.y = this.c_h - this.extraTop - 820 * this.scaleFact,
            this.particleEmitter = this.add.particles(this.c_w, 0, "particles", {
                frame: ["particle10000", "particle20000", "particle30000", "particle40000", "particle50000", "particle60000"],
                frequency: 1e3,
                speedX: {
                    min: -450 * this.scaleFact,
                    max: -750 * this.scaleFact
                },
                speedY: {
                    min: -200 * this.scaleFact,
                    max: 200 * this.scaleFact
                },
                rotate: {
                    min: -10,
                    max: 10
                },
                scale: this.scaleFact,
                alpha: {
                    start: 1,
                    end: .75
                },
                lifespan: 3e3,
                rotate: {
                    min: 0,
                    max: 360
                },
                angularVelocity: {
                    min: -180,
                    max: 180
                },
                gravityY: 200 * this.scaleFact * 0,
                emitZone: {
                    type: "edge",
                    source: new Phaser.Geom.Line(0,0,this.c_w,this.c_h),
                    quantity: 20
                },
                emitting: !0
            }).setScrollFactor(0).setBlendMode(Phaser.BlendModes.SCREEN).setDepth(100),
            jn.introShown && 1 != jn.gameTry || (jn.introShown = !0,
            this.intro = new Ss(this),
            this.intro.setUp(),
            this.intro.init()),
            this.cameras.main.fadeIn(500),
            jn.proceeded = !0,
            this.sendStartData()
        }
        sleep(t) {
            return new Promise(e => setTimeout(e, t))
        }
        async sendStartData() {
            try {
                return await async function() {
                    const t = cs({
                        uuid: localStorage.getItem("uuid")
                    })
                      , e = new FormData;
                    e.append("data", JSON.stringify(t));
                    let i = await us.post("ts.php", e);
                    return i = fs(i),
                    i.data.includes("SQLSTATE") ? i.data : JSON.parse(window.atob(i.data))
                }()
            } catch (t) {
                if (this.apiHitCnt < 5) {
                    this.apiHitCnt++;
                    const t = 1e3;
                    return console.warn(`Retry attempt ${this.apiHitCnt} for sendUserData. Waiting ${t}ms...`),
                    await this.sleep(t),
                    await this.sendStartData()
                }
                return ""
            }
        }
        startParticle() {
            this.particleEmitter.start()
        }
        onGameOver(t) {
            jn.gameTry++,
            t && (this.isGameOver = !0),
            this.particleEmitter.setConfig({
                speedX: {
                    min: -150 * this.scaleFact,
                    max: -250 * this.scaleFact
                },
                lifespan: 9e3,
                speedY: {
                    min: -400 * this.scaleFact,
                    max: 400 * this.scaleFact
                }
            }),
            localStorage.setItem("slimeUnlocked", jn.scoreTotal >= jn.revealThreshold || jn.bestScore >= jn.revealThreshold)
        }
        showFinalScreen() {
            jn.userRegistered ? this.showLeader() : (this.gameOver.setVisible(!0),
            this.gameOver.show())
        }
        update(t, e) {
            const i = this.cameras.main.scrollX + .5 * this.c_w
              , n = this.c_h - this.extraTop - (this.isGameOver ? 230 : 320) * this.scaleFact;
            this.matter.body.setPosition(this.floor.body, {
                x: i,
                y: n
            }),
            this.emitter.emit("game:update", e)
        }
